==English==
===Pronunciation===
* /ˈɡʌvi/

===Etymology===
Diminutive in [[-y]] from [[government]].

===Adjective===
'''govvy'''
# ''(colloquial)'' Of or run by the government.

===Noun===
'''govvy''' ''(plural:'' '''govvies''')
# A government job.

