===History===

The use of the word, '''govvy''' is in essence a slang word. There where limited quotes and references post around the internet on forums, but over the past ten years its use has increased. There are other elements that have helped the word to be more used and one could be that it has been used as a nickname and the owner refered people to its meaning allowing it to be used.